# modules/ — optional domain extensions
#
# Add subdirectories here for optional capabilities that extend the core agent layer.
# Each module is self-contained: its own skills/, config, and README.
#
# Example:
#   modules/financial-nlp/   — FinBERT sentiment analysis
#   modules/data-pipeline/   — ETL utilities
#   modules/reporting/       — output formatting and charting
#
# A module is only loaded when explicitly requested. It does not affect core behaviour.
